<div>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.1 (STRIPS 1-2) JI XUSHENG4:158">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-1a.1">魯莊公將爲大鐘,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-1a.2">型既成矣.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-1a.3">曹沫入見,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-1a.4">曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-1a.5">“昔周室之封魯,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-1a.6">東西七百,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-1a.7">南北五百,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-1a.8">非(匪)山非(匪)澤,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-1a.9">無有不民.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-1a.10">今邦彌小</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-1a.11">而鐘愈大，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-1a.12">君其圖之.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.2 (STRIPS 2-3) JI XUSHENG4:158">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-2a.1">昔堯之饗舜也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-2a.2">飯於土簋,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-2a.3">欲(=飲)於土鉶,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-2a.4">而撫有天下.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-2a.5">此不貧於美</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-2a.6">而富於德歟?</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.3 (STRIPS 3, 41) JI XUSHENG4:158">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-3a.1">昔周[室] [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-3a.2">[...] 境必勝,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-3a.3">可以有治邦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-3a.4">周志是存.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.4 (STRIPS 41, 4, 5) JI XUSHENG4:158">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-4a.1">莊公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-4a.2">“[...]今天下之君子既可知已,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-4a.3">孰能并兼人哉?”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.5 (STRIPS 5-6) JI XUSHENG4:158-159">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-5a.1">曹沫曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-5a.2">“君其毋愪.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-5a.3">臣聞之曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-5a.4">鄰邦之君明,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-5a.5">則不可以不修政</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-5a.6">而善於民,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-5a.7">不然恐亡焉.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-5a.8">鄰邦之君無道,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-5a.9">則亦不可以不修政</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-5a.10">而善於民.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-5a.11">不然無以取之.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.6 (STRIPS 6, 7A) JI XUSHENG4:159">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-6a.1">莊公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-6a.2">“昔施伯語寡人曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-6a.3">‘君子得之失之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-6a.4">天命.’</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-6a.5">今異於爾言.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.7 (STRIPS 7A, 8B, 9, 10) JI XUSHENG4:159">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-7a.1">曹沫曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-7a.2">“[...]無以異於臣之言,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-7a.3">君弗盡.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-7a.4">臣聞之曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-7a.5">君子以賢稱而失之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-7a.6">天命;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-7a.7">以亡道稱</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-7a.8">而沒身就世,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-7a.9">亦天命.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-7a.10">不然君子以賢稱,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-7a.11">曷有弗得?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-7a.12">以無道稱,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-7a.13">曷有弗失?”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.8 (STRIPS 10, 11, 12) JI XUSHENG4:159">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-8a.1">莊公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-8a.2">“慢哉,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-8a.3">吾聞此言.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-8a.4">乃命毀鐘型</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-8a.5">而聽邦政.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-8a.6">不晝寢,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-8a.7">不飲酒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-8a.8">不聽樂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-8a.9">居不褻文,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-8a.10">食不貳菜,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-8a.11">[...] 兼愛萬民</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-8a.12">而無有私也.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.9 (STRIPS 12-13) JI XUSHENG4:168">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-9a.1">還年而問於曹沫曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-9a.2">“吾欲與齊戰,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-9a.3">問陣奚如?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-9a.4">守邊城奚如?”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.10 (STRIPS 13-14) JI XUSHENG4:168">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-10a.1">曹沫答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-10a.2">“臣聞之:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-10a.3">有固謀,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-10a.4">而無固城;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-10a.5">有克政,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-10a.6">而無克陣.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-10a.7">三代之陣皆存,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-10a.8">或以克,或以亡.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.11 (STRIPS 14, 17, 18) JI XUSHENG4:168-169">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-11a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-11a.1">且臣聞之:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-11a.2">小邦處大邦之間,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-11a.3">敵邦交地,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-11a.4">不可以先作怨,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-11a.5">疆地毋先而必取[.]焉,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-11a.6">所以距邊;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-11a.7">毋愛貨資子女,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-11a.8">以事其便嬖,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-11a.9">所以距內;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-11a.10">城郭必修,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-11a.11">繕甲利兵,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-11a.12">必有戰心以守,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-11a.13">所以爲長也.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.12 (STRIPS 18-20) JI XUSHENG4:169">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-12a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-12a.1">且臣之聞之:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-12a.2">不和於邦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-12a.3">不可以出豫.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-12a.4">不和於豫,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-12a.5">不可以出陣.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-12a.6">不和於陣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-12a.7">不可以戰.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-12a.8">是故夫陣者,三教之末.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-12a.9">君必不已,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-12a.10">則由其本乎?”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.13 (STRIPS 20-21) JI XUSHENG4:177">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-13a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-13a.1">莊公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-13a.2">“爲和於邦如之何?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-13a.3">曹沫答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-13a.4">“毋獲民時,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-13a.5">毋奪民利,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-13a.6">陳功而食,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-13a.7">刑罰有罪</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-13a.8">而賞爵有德.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.15 (STRIPS 22, 25, 23B) JI XUSHENG4:177">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-14a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-14a.1">莊公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-14a.2">“爲和於豫如何?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-14a.3">曹沫曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-14a.4">“三軍出,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-14a.5">君自率,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-14a.6">必有二將軍,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-14a.7">每將軍必有數嬖大夫,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-14a.8">每嬖大夫 必有數大官之師,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-14a.9">公孫公子.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-14a.10">凡有司率長,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-14a.11">[...] 期會之不難;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-14a.12">所以爲和於豫.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.16 (STRIPS 23B, 24A, 30, 26) JI XUSHENG4:177">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-15a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-15a.1">莊公又問:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-15a.2">“爲和於陣如何?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-15a.3">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-15a.4">“車間容伍,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-15a.5">伍間容兵,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-15a.6">貴位,重食,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-15a.7">使爲前行.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-15a.8">三行之後,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-15a.9">後見短兵,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-15a.10">什伍之間必有公孫公子,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-15a.11">是謂軍紀.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.17 (STRIPS 26, 62, 58) JI XUSHENG4:177-178">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-16a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-16a.1">五人以伍,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-16a.2">一人有多,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-16a.3">四人皆賞,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-16a.4">所以爲斷.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-16a.5">毋尚獲</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-16a.6">而尚聞命,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-16a.7">所以爲毋退.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-16a.8">率車以車,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-16a.9">率徒以徒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-16a.10">所以同死.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.18 (STRIPS 37B, 38) JI XUSHENG4:178">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-17a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-17a.1">有戒言曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-17a.2">‘奔</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-17a.3">尔定訌;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-17a.4">不奔,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-17a.5">而或興,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-17a.6">或康以會.’</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-17a.7">故帥不使奔,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-17a.8">奔則不行.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-17a.9">戰有顯道,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-17a.10">勿兵以克.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.19 (STRIPS 38-40) JI XUSHENG4:178">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-18a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-18a.1">莊公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-18a.2">“勿兵以克奚如?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-18a.3">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-18a.4">“人之兵不砥礪,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-18a.5">兵必砥礪.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-18a.6">人之甲不堅,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-18a.7">我甲必堅.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-18a.8">人使士,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-18a.9">我使大夫.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-18a.10">人使大夫,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-18a.11">我使將軍.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-18a.12">人使將軍,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-18a.13">我君身進.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-18a.14">此戰之顯道.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.20 (STRIPS 40, 42) JI XUSHENG4:189-190">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-19a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-19a.1">莊公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-19a.2">“既成教矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-19a.3">出師有機乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-19a.4">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-19a.5">“有.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-19a.6">臣聞之:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-19a.7">三軍出,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-19a.8">其將卑,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-19a.9">父兄不薦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-19a.10">由邦御之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-19a.11">此出師之機.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.21 (STRIPS 42-43) JI XUSHENG4:190">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-20a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-20a.1">莊公又問曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-20a.2">“三軍散裹(?)</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-20a.3">有機乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-20a.4">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-20a.5">“有.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-20a.6">臣聞之:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-20a.7">三軍未成陣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-20a.8">未豫,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-20a.9">行阪濟障,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-20a.10">此散裹(?)之機.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.22 (STRIPS 43-44) JI XUSHENG4:190">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-21a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-21a.1">莊公又問曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-21a.2">“戰有機乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-21a.3">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-21a.4">“有.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-21a.5">其去之不速,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-21a.6">其就之不傅,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-21a.7">其啓節不疾,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-21a.8">此戰之機.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-21a.9">是故疑陣敗,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-21a.10">疑戰死.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.23 (STRIPS 44-45) JI XUSHENG4:190">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-22a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-22a.1">莊公又問曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-22a.2">“既戰有機乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-22a.3">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-22a.4">“有.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-22a.5">其賞鮮且不中,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-22a.6">其誅重且不察,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-22a.7">死者弗收,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-22a.8">傷者弗問,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-22a.9">既戰</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-22a.10">而有怠心,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-22a.11">此既戰之機.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.24 (STRIPS 45, 46A, 47) JI XUSHENG4:197">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-23a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-23a.1">莊公又問曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-23a.2">“復敗戰有道乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-23a.3">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-23a.4">“有.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-23a.5">三軍大敗,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-23a.6">[死]者收之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-23a.7">傷者問之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-23a.8">善於死者</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-23a.9">爲生者.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.25 (STRIPS 47, 63A, 27) JI XUSHENG4:197">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-24a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-24a.1">君乃自過,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-24a.2">以悅於萬民,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-24a.3">弗狎危地(?),</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-24a.4">毋火食,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-24a.5">[毋]誅而賞,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-24a.6">毋罪百姓,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-24a.7">而改其將.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.26 (STRIPS 27, 23A, 51B) JI XUSHENG4:197">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-25a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-25a.1">君如親率,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-25a.2">必聚群有司而告之:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-25a.3">‘二三子勉之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-25a.4">過不在子,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-25a.5">在寡人.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-25a.6">吾戰適不順於天命,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-25a.7">反師</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-25a.8">將復戰.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.27 (STRIPS 29, 24B, 50) JI XUSHENG4:197-198">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-26a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-26a.1">必召邦之貴人及邦之奇士</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-26a.2">御卒使兵,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-26a.3">毋復前常.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-26a.4">凡貴人使處前位一行,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-26a.5">後則見亡.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-26a.6">進則祿爵有常,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-26a.7">機莫之當.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.28 (STRIPS 50, 51A, 31) JI XUSHENG4:198">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-27a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-27a.1">莊公又問曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-27a.2">“復盤(?)戰有道乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-27a.3">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-27a.4">“有.“</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-27a.5">既戰</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-27a.6">復舍,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-27a.7">號令於軍中曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-27a.8">“繕甲利兵,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-27a.9">明日將戰.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-27a.10">廝徒煬,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-27a.11">以盤就行</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-27a.12">失車甲,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-27a.13">命之毋行.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.29 (STRIPS 31-32) JI XUSHENG4:198">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-28a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-28a.1">明日將戰,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-28a.2">使爲前行.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-28a.3">諜人來告曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-28a.4">“其將帥盡傷,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-28a.5">車輦皆栽(with no 木)</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-28a.6">曰將早行.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-28a.7">乃[命]白徒</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-28a.8">早食</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-28a.9">輂兵,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-28a.10">各載尔藏.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.30 (STRIPS 32B, 52, 53A) JI XUSHENG4:198">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-29a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-29a.1">既戰</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-29a.2">將量,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-29a.3">爲之毋怠,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-29a.4">毋使民疑.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-29a.5">及尔龜筮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-29a.6">皆曰勝之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-29a.7">改冒尔鼓,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-29a.8">乃秩其備.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-29a.9">明日復陣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-29a.10">必過其所.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-29a.11">此復盤戰之道.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.31 (STRIPS 53A, 60B) JI XUSHENG4:198">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-30a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-30a.1">莊公又問曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-30a.2">“復甘戰有道乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-30a.3">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-30a.4">“有.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-30a.5">必慎以戒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-30a.6">如將弗克?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-30a.7">毋冒以陷,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-30a.8">必過前攻.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.32 (STRIPS 61, 53B) JI XUSHENG4:198-9">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-31a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-31a.1">賞獲,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-31a.2">飭葸,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-31a.3">以勸其志.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-31a.4">勇者喜之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-31a.5">惶者悔之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-31a.6">萬民貢首,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-31a.7">皆欲克之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-31a.8">此復甘戰之道.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.33 (STRIPS 53B, 54) JI XUSHENG4:199">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-32a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-32a.1">莊公又問曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-32a.2">“復苦戰有道乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-32a.3">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-32a.4">“有.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-32a.5">收而聚之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-32a.6">束而厚之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-32a.7">重賞薄刑,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-32a.8">使忘其死</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-32a.9">而獻其生,</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.34 (STRIPS 54-55) JI XUSHENG4:199">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-33a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-33a.1">使良車 良士往取餌,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-33a.2">使其志起,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-33a.3">勇者使喜,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-33a.4">葸者使悔,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-33a.5">然後改始.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-33a.6">此復苦戰之道.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.35 (STRIPS 55-57) JI XUSHENG4:218">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-34a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-34a.1">莊公又問曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-34a.2">“善攻者奚如?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-34a.3">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-34a.4">“民有寶,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-34a.5">曰城,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-34a.6">曰固,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-34a.7">曰阻.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-34a.8">三者盡用</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-34a.9">不棄,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-34a.10">邦家以宏.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-34a.11">善攻者必以其所有,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-34a.12">以攻人之所亡有.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.36 (STRIPS 57, 15-16, 46B) JI XUSHENG4:218-9">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-35a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-35a.1">莊公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-35a.2">“善守者奚如?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-35a.3">答曰: He answered:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-35a.4">“其食足以食之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-35a.5">其兵足以利之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-35a.6">其城固足以捍之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-35a.7">上下和且篤,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-35a.8">繲(絓)紀於大國,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-35a.9">大國親之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-35a.10">天下不勝.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.37 (STRIPS 46B, 33) JI XUSHENG4:219">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-36a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-36a.1">卒欲少以多,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-36a.2">少則易察,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-36a.3">迄成則易治,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-36a.4">果勝矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-36a.5">親率勝.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-36a.6">使人,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-36a.7">不親則不敦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-36a.8">不和則不篤,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-36a.9">不義則不服.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.38 (STRIPS 33-35) JI XUSHENG4:224">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-37a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-37a.1">莊公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-37a.2">“爲親如何?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-37a.3">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-37a.4">“君毋憚自勞,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-37a.5">以觀上下之情僞;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-37a.6">匹夫寡婦之獄訟,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-37a.7">君必身聽之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-37a.8">有知不足,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-37a.9">無所不中,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-37a.10">則民親之.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.39 (STRIPS 35-36) JI XUSHENG4:224">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-38a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-38a.1">莊公又問:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-38a.2">“爲和如何?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-38a.3">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-38a.4">“毋嬖於便嬖,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-38a.5">毋長於父兄,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-38a.6">賞均聽中,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-38a.7">則民和之.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.40 (STRIPS 36, 28) JI XUSHENG4:224">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-39a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-39a.1">莊公又問:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-39a.2">“爲義如何?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-39a.3">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-39a.4">“陳功尚賢.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-39a.5">能治百人,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-39a.6">使長百人;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-39a.7">能治三軍,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-39a.8">使帥.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-39a.9">授有智,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-39a.10">予有能,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-39a.11">則民義之.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.41 (STRIPS 28, 37A, 49) JI XUSHENG4:224-5">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-40a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-40a.1">且臣聞之:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-40a.2">卒有長,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-40a.3">三軍有率帥,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-40a.4">邦有君,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-40a.5">此三者所以戰.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-40a.6">是故長民者毋攝爵,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-40a.7">毋御軍,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-40a.8">毋避罪,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-40a.9">用都教於邦於民.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.42 (STRIPS 49, 48, 59) JI XUSHENG4:225">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-41a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-41a.1">莊公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-41a.2">“此三者足以戰乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-41a.3">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-41a.4">“戒.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-41a.5">勝不可不慎.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-41a.6">不卒</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-41a.7">不恒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-41a.8">不和</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-41a.9">則不篤,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-41a.10">不謙畏 [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-41a.11">[...] 其志者,寡矣.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.43 (STRIPS 59, 60A) JI XUSHENG4:229">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-42a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-42a.1">莊公又問曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-42a.2">“吾有所聞之:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-42a.3">一出言三軍皆勸,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-42a.4">一出言三軍皆往,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-42a.5">有之乎?”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.44 (STRIPS 60A, 63A, 64) JI XUSHENG4:230 TR. CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-43a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-43a.1">答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-43a.2">“有.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-43a.3">盟衁 (?)鬼神</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-43a.4">忽武,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-43a.5">非所以教民,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-43a.6">[.]君其知之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-43a.7">此先王之至道.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.45 (STRIPS 64-65A) JI XUSHENG4:230 TR. CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-44a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-44a.1">莊公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-44a.2">“沫,吾言寔不,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-44a.3">而毋惑諸小道歟?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-44a.4">吾一欲聞三代之所.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-44a.5">曹沫答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-44a.6">“臣聞之:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-44a.7">昔之明王之起於天下者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-44a.8">各以其世,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-44a.9">以及其身.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CAOMOZHICHEN 4.21.46 (STRIPS 65A, 7B, 8A, 65B) JI XUSHENG4:230">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-45a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-45a.1">今與古亦間不同矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-45a.2">臣是故不敢以古答.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-45a.3">然而古亦有大道焉,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-45a.4">必恭儉以得之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-45a.5">而驕泰以失之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0050_tls_001-45a.6">君[其]亦唯聞夫禹, 湯, 桀, 纣矣.</seg>
                </p>

